{
  "chapter": "051",
  "title": "荆燕世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">荆王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>，是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸刘</span>宗室，不知他最初起兵时是哪一支。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，回军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>塞地，从东边<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>，向北渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张耳</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>的军队，驻军在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">脩武</span>，挖深壕沟、筑高壁垒，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二万人</span>、<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百</span>骑，渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白马津</span>进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地，焚烧楚军的积粮，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破坏</span>楚军的生业，使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>军队无粮可供。不久<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘贾\">贾（刘贾）</span>总是坚守壁垒不肯与楚<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">交战</span>，而与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>互相策应。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>追击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">固陵</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>向南渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寿春</span>。到了之后，派人暗中招降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周殷</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周殷</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，协助<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>攻取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>，迎接<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王黥布</span>的军队，都会合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垓下</span>，一起<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>率领<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>的军队，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>向西南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">临江王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共尉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共尉</span>被杀之后，改<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">临江</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南郡</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">春</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>地会合<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，废黜<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>禁他，把他的封地分为两个国。当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的儿子年幼，昆弟很少，又不贤能，想<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">同姓</span>为王以镇抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，于是下诏说：\"将军<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>有功，以及挑选子弟中可以为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的人。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都说：\"<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">荆王</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">统领</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮东</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十二城</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘交\">交（刘交）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">统领</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮西</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十六城</span>。\"于是又立儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘肥\">肥（刘肥）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>。这是首次将<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>兄弟<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">秋</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛，向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">荆</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">荆王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘贾\">贾（刘贾）</span>与他<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">交战</span>，没能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取胜</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逃</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">富陵</span>，被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>的军队<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>害。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>亲自率军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">沛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘濞</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">统领</span>原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">荆</span>的地盘。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘泽</span>，是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸刘</span>远房宗室。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>身份<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>，俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">营陵侯</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">高后时</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>游说缺乏财资，以计策求见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">营陵侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>很喜欢他，用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百斤</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>祝寿。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>得到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>后，立即回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>派人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>说：\"咱们断交算了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>于是到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，不去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>，却租借大宅，让他的儿子去求事<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>所宠幸的大<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张子卿</span>。过了几个月，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>的儿子请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>光临，亲自准备。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>答应前往。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>盛陈<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帷帐</span>和器具，跟<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>一样。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>很吃惊。酒正畅时，他屏退左右游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>说：\"我看过<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的府邸有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀</span>所，都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>当年所有的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>。如今<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>本是推戴<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>夺取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>的，功劳极大，又有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>身份的分量。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>年纪大了，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>势弱，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>想<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕产</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">统领</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>地。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>却又顾虑此事难办，担心<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>不答应。如今您最得宠，又是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>们所敬重的，何不暗示<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>知道他们会支持，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>必定高兴。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>一旦<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯</span>也是您的囊中之物了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>心中是想这样做的，可您作为内臣，不赶紧提议，恐怕祸患要临到您自己了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>非常赞同，于是暗示<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>进言。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>临朝时，便问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>请求<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕产</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吕王</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>赏赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千斤</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>把其中一半给了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>不肯接受，趁机又劝他说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕产</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>了，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸大臣</span>还不完全信服。如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">营陵侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>，是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸刘</span>宗室，又担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>，只有他还有怨望之心。如果您向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>进言，划出<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀县</span>让他<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>，他得到了<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>爵就会高兴地离去，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>的<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>就更加稳固了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>入宫进言，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>同意了。于是封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">营陵侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘泽</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">琅邪王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">琅邪王</span>就与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">前往封国</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>赶紧赶路，不要停留。出了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>果然派人追去想留住他，但他已经出关，使者只好返回。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>去世，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">琅邪王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>就说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>年幼，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>掌权，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>孤立势弱。\"于是率兵与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>合谋向西，打算<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>。行至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁</span>，听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派遣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌将军</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">驻</span>屯<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>便<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">返</span>回军队<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">守备</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西界</span>，然后轻骑急驰赶到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>也从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>地赶到。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将相</span>和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">琅邪王</span>共同<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>于是改封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>，把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">琅邪</span>还给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，恢复其旧地。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">统领</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">敬王（刘泽）</span>。传给儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘嘉\">嘉（刘嘉）</span>，是为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘嘉\">康王（刘嘉）</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到他的孙子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定国</span>时，与父亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘嘉\">康王（刘嘉）</span>的姬妾私通，生了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一个</span>男孩。又夺弟弟的妻子为姬妾。又与<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三个</span>女儿私通。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定国</span>想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他的臣子<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">肥如</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郢人</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郢人</span>等告发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定国</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定国</span>便指使<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span>以其他罪名弹劾逮捕并格<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郢人</span>以灭口。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元朔元年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郢人</span>的兄弟再次上书详细陈述<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定国</span>的阴私事，因此事情被揭发。诏令交付<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>议论，都说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定国</span>行为如禽兽，扰乱人伦，违逆<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天</span>道，应当<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>批准了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定国</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>改为郡。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">荆王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>，是因为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>初<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>尚未安定，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>虽然宗属疏远，也能凭计策<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，镇抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>一带。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘泽</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>，是用权术激动<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>的结果，然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘泽</span>最终<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">南面</span>称君达<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三代</span>。事情激发而相互看重，岂不是很了不起吗！"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>最初跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>，首先<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。 渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白马</span>津后，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寿春</span>。 接着迎接<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>，离间<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周殷</span>反楚。 论功封土，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>相邻。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">营陵</span>初封，功勋源于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">陈（陈豨）</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田生</span>游说成功，获赐<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千斤</span>黄金。 以权术激动<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>，事情成而显荣自身。 改封传续子嗣，最终因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郢人</span>之事而国亡。"
